<plot>Benny Lugo is twenty-seven years old and unmotivated. He spends the better part of every day just sitting in his parent's livingroom. When he isn't doing that, he is usually out playing basketball or trying to outsmart his parents, who are insistent that he find a job. Along with his friend Danny, they devise a method for avoiding the pretense of pretending to be looking for work.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?016078</url></doc>
